{"_id":"note:4Deq7NUe_w","title":"Forms","content":"## HTML Forms\n\n\n\n\n- Method : HTTP Verb / Post / Get\n- Action : Where the data is going to\n- type: defines the type of input to be rendered\n- name: without name data won't be sent to the server\n- value: data that is sent to the server \n- name=\"value\"\n\n\n```html \n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"style.css\">\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Rubik\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <title>Password Input</title>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n    <section id=\"overlay\">\n        <img src=\"https://content.codecademy.com/courses/web-101/unit-6/htmlcss1-img_burger-logo.svg\"\n            alt=\"Davie's Burgers Logo\" id=\"logo\">\n        <hr>\n        <form action=\"\" method=\"post\">\n            <h1>Login to start creating a burger!</h1>\n\n            <!-- User name Text Input-->\n            <label for=\"username\">Username:</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" name=\"username\" id=\"username\">\n\n\n            <br>\n\n            <!-- Password Input -->\n            <label for=\"user-pw\">Password:</label>\n            <input type=\"password\" name=\"user-pw\" id=\"user-pw\">\n\n            <h1>Create a burger!</h1>\n\n            <!-- Dropdown Input -->\n            <section class=\"protein\">\n                <label for=\"patty\">What type of protein would you like?</label>\n                <select id=\"patty\" name=\"protein\">\n                    <option value=\"beef\">Beef</option>\n                    <option value=\"chicken\">Chick</option>\n                    <option value=\"fish\">Fish</option>\n                    <option value=\"vegan\">Vegan</option>\n                </select>\n\n            </section>\n            <hr>\n\n            <!-- Number Input -->\n\n            <section class=\"patties\">\n                <label for=\"amount\">How many patties would you like?</label>\n                <input type=\"number\" name=\"amount\" id=\"amount\" step=\"1\">\n            </section>\n            <hr>\n\n            <!-- Range Input -->\n            <section class=\"cooked\">\n                <label for=\"doneness\">How do you want your patty cooked</label>\n                <br>\n                <span>Rare</span>\n                <input type=\"range\" id=\"doneness\" name=\"doneness\" min=\"0\" max=\"5\" step=\"0.5\">\n                <span>Well-Done</span>\n            </section>\n            <hr>\n\n            <!-- Checkbox Input -->\n\n            <section class=\"toppings\">\n                <span>What toppings would you like?</span>\n                <br>\n\n                <label for=\"lettuce\">Lettuce</label>\n                <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topping\" value=\"lettuce\" id=\"lettuce\">\n\n                <label for=\"tomato\">Tomato</label>\n                <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topping\" value=\"tomato\" id=\"tomato\">\n\n\n                <label for=\"onion\">Onion</label>\n                <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"topping\" value=\"onion\" id=\"onion\">\n\n            </section>\n\n\n            <!-- Radio Input -->\n\n            <section class=\"cheesy\">\n                <span>Would you like to add cheese?</span>\n                <br>\n                <label for=\"yes\">Yes</label>\n                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"cheese\" id=\"yes\" value=\"yes\">\n                <label for=\"no\">No</label>\n                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"cheese\" id=\"no\" value=\"no\">\n            </section>\n\n\n            <!-- Select List (No Filter) -->\n\n            <section class=\"bun-type\">\n                <label for=\"bun\">What type of bun would you like?</label>\n                <select name=\"bun\" id=\"bun\">\n                    <option value=\"sesame\">Sesame</option>\n                    <option value=\"potato\">Potato</option>\n                    <option value=\"plain\">Plain</option>\n                </select>\n\n            </section>\n\n            <!-- Data List (Filter) -->\n\n            <section class=\"sauce-selection\">\n\n                <label for=\"sauce\">What type of sauce would you like?</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"sauce\" list=\"sauces\" id=\"sauce\">\n\n                <datalist id=\"sauces\">\n                    <option value=\"Ketchup\"></option>\n                    <option value=\"Mayo\"></option>\n                    <option value=\"Mustard\"></option>\n                </datalist>\n\n            </section>\n\n\n            <!--  Text Area Input -->\n\n            <section class=\"extra-info\">\n\n                <label for=\"extra\">Anything else you want to add?</label>\n                <textarea name=\"extra\" id=\"extra\" cols=\"40\" rows=\"3\">This is just default text\n                </textarea>\n\n            </section>\n\n            <!--  Submit Button -->\n\n            <section class=\"submission\">\n                <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" class=\"btn\">\n            </section>\n\n\n\n        </form>\n    </section>\n</body>\n\n</html>\n\n```\n","tags":[],"folderPathname":"/ðŸ“˜ FrontEnd/HTML","data":{},"createdAt":"2022-07-04T11:22:13.702Z","updatedAt":"2022-07-05T07:17:35.582Z","trashed":false,"_rev":"d3gDN4r_A"}